Package: resizer
Title: Simulate Screen Resolution for Shiny Application
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Victor", "Perrier", email = "victor.perrier@dreamrs.fr", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Fanny", "Meyer", role = "aut"),
  person("David", "Granjon", role = "aut"),
  person("David", "J. Bradshaw", role = c("cph"), comment = "iframe-resizer library"))
Description: When developing applications, the display may be different depending on 
  the screen on which the application is displayed. This application allows you to simulate
  different resolutions to verify that the display is correct.
